<li>
Effectively applies our methodology and enforces project standards.</li>
<li>
Minimizes our exposure and risk on each project managed by monitoring project profitability, revenue, bill rates and utilization and reporting any irregularities to the Team Lead.</li>
<li>
Ensures project documents are complete, current, and stored appropriately (Meeting agendas, Status reports, etc.).</li>
<li>
Manages team and company systems including Openair and Central Desktop to ensure proper management of project budgets.</li>
<li>
Communication</li>
<li>
Facilitates team and client meetings effectively by preparing agendas, conference reports and project status reports.</li>
<li>
Holds regular status meetings with project team to ensure projects are on time and within budget.</li>
<li>
Effectively communicates relevant project information to superiors.</li>
<li>
Resolves and/or escalates resourcing, budget, and other issues in a timely fashion.</li>
</ul>
